                  <summary><p>A multi-text manuscript  (possibly a composite manuscript) containing:
<list rend="numbered">
     <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Akattiyatiraṭṭu</title>, a selection of 25 <title xml:lang="ta">Tēvāram</title> hymns, traditionally associated with Akattiyar (U2).</item>
  <item>A selection of 6 hymns from the <title xml:lang="ta">Tiruvācakam</title> (U3).</item>
  <item>A selection of 14 (?) hymns from the <title xml:lang="ta">Tēvāram</title> (U4).</item>
  </list>
See Chevillard (2020).</p>

<p>Description based on the examination of the original manuscript (May 2023).</p>   <p>Dimensions assessed at the time of examination.</p></summary>
                  
